OL,3,CBirmingham City Council settles
OL,4,Chistoric equal pay claim after
OL,5,Cbankruptcy
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council has reached an
OL,8,Fagreement to settle thousands of equal
OL,9,Fpay claims that have pushed the local
OL,10,Fauthority to the brink of bankruptcy.
OL,12,FThe announcement comes just a day
OL,13,Fafter ITV News' Deputy Political
OL,14,FEditor Anushka Asthana reports
OL,15,FBirmingham Council is poised to pay
OL,16,Fout hundreds of millions of pounds to
OL,17,Fwomen workers including teaching
OL,18,Fassistants and cleaners.
