OL,7,FIn a statement issued on Tuesday, the
OL,8,Flocal authority said a paper related
OL,9,Fto the "framework agreement" will be
OL,10,Fput before its cabinet committee next
OL,11,Fweek to seek formal approval for the
OL,12,Fplan.
OL,14,FThe full terms of the settlement
OL,15,Freached with GMB and Unison are
OL,16,Fconfidential, but the council said the
OL,17,Fcost of the settlement falls within
OL,18,Fthe limit of an Exceptional Financial
OL,19,FSupport package agreed with the
OL,20,Fprevious government in January.
