OL,7,FGMB Union said the agreement meant
OL,8,Fthat, four years after launching their
OL,9,Fcampaign, 6,000 low-paid,
OL,10,Fpredominantly women workers look set
OL,11,Fto finally receive settlement payments
OL,12,Ffrom the local authority.
OL,14,FSettlement payouts are expected to be
OL,15,Fup to four times higher than the
OL,16,Fpayment offered to workers in 2021,
OL,17,Fwith settlement expected to take place
OL,18,Fin the middle of 2025, the union said.
