OL,7,FCouncillor John Cotton, Leader of
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council said: "This
OL,9,Fframework agreement marks the end of
OL,10,Fan intense period of dialogue between
OL,11,Fthe council and its unions.
OL,13,F"It is an important step on the
OL,14,Fcouncil's improvement journey. I would
OL,15,Flike to put on record my thanks to GMB
OL,16,Fand UNISON for the constructive way in
OL,17,Fwhich they have approached these
OL,18,Fnegotiations."
