OL,7,F"I was appointed as Leader to end the
OL,8,Ffailings within this council that led
OL,9,Fto the equal pay liability and this
OL,10,Fframework agreement is intended to
OL,11,Fmark the start of a new era of
OL,12,Fproductive and progressive industrial
OL,13,Frelations built on trust and mutual
OL,14,Frespect.
