OL,7,F"The Council is facing unprecedented
OL,8,Fchallenges. It will only get through
OL,9,Fthis period by working collaboratively
OL,10,Fwith its staff and their union
OL,11,Frepresentatives to focus upon
OL,12,Fdelivering the best possible outcome
OL,13,Ffor communities across the city.
OL,15,F"The next phase of the equal pay
OL,16,Fprogramme will be to deliver a new pay
OL,17,Fand grading model and job evaluation
OL,18,Fscheme so that pay inequality at the
OL,19,Fcity council can end once and for all."
