OL,7,FRhea Wolfson, GMB's head of
OL,8,Findustrials relations, described the
OL,9,Fagreement as a "historic outcome" for
OL,10,Fwomen employed by the council.
OL,12,F"This result would not have happened
OL,13,Fwithout their dedicated and tireless
OL,14,Fleadership of a campaign which has
OL,15,Fovercome huge odds," she said.
