OL,7,FAlice Reynolds, GMB Organiser, said:
OL,8,F"The women of Birmingham City Council
OL,9,Fhave delivered an historic outcome
OL,10,Ftoday. "This agreement would not have
OL,11,Fhappened without the determination
OL,12,Fshown by low paid women workers.
OL,14,F"In schools, offices and workplaces
OL,15,Facross our City, GMB members have led
OL,16,Fthe fight for equal pay.
OL,18,F"Now this Framework Agreement sets out
OL,19,Fa cast iron plan to settle our
OL,20,Fmembers' claims and pay back their
OL,21,Fwages after years of discrimination.
