OL,7,F"Pay justice for Birmingham's women
OL,8,Fworkers is something that our union
OL,9,Fhas long led the fight for; today this
OL,10,FFramework Agreement brings that within
OL,11,Ftouching distance".
OL,13,FUNISON West Midlands head of
OL,14,Forganising Claire Campbell said: "This
OL,15,Fis a good day for low-paid women who
OL,16,Fwork at the council. They will at last
OL,17,Fget the pay justice they deserve.
